title: Disney - Dive into Disney
description:
From Wikipedia:

Dive into Disney is a Japanese album containing rock/ska renditions of various Disney songs, such as Mickey Mouse Club March, Hakuna Matata, and It&#039;s a Small World, performed by various artists. Because the entire album contains Disney songs, most of the songs are in English, not Japanese.
